and I killed my mother.</i>

01:21.054 --> 01:23.353
<i>I had her sliced open,</i>

01:23.355 --> 01:26.120
<i>like a goat for the slaughter,
to get me pulled out.</i>

01:27.487 --> 01:31.086
<i>As she bled, the doctor
pushed air into my lungs,</i>

01:31.088 --> 01:34.220
<i>and pressed his hands
repeatedly onto my chest,</i>

01:34.222 --> 01:37.120
<i>with the same rhythmic,
repetitive motion</i>

01:37.122 --> 01:40.053
<i>that he used to jerk himself
off that very morning.</i>

01:42.620 --> 01:43.686
<i>It worked.</i>

01:45.288 --> 01:47.353
<i>He came and I came...
Back to life.</i>

01:53.187 --> 01:56.220
<i>The fact that my mother
lost her life for this,</i>

01:56.222 --> 01:58.986
<i>for me, is probably
just a side note.</i>

01:58.988 --> 02:01.086
<i>The cost of doing business.</i>

02:06.154 --> 02:08.220
<i>But it's me who pays.</i>

02:08.487 --> 02:11.320
<i>It's on my tab.</i>

02:11.322 --> 02:14.419
<i>And it accumulates interest
with every passing year.</i>

02:37.487 --> 02:41.186
<i>My point is,
there's no place for me.</i>

02:41.188 --> 02:45.020
<i>Because I'm not
supposed to be here.</i>

02:45.022 --> 02:49.920
<i>Maybe if I was some sort of Olympic
athlete, or a genius scientist,</i>

02:49.922 --> 02:52.053
<i>but I'm not.</i>

02:52.055 --> 02:54.686
<i>I'm not any of those things.</i>

02:54.688 --> 02:59.586
<i>I'm just a girl.
A murderer without a motive.</i>

02:59.588 --> 03:05.319
<i>So I serve my time, waiting
for my sentence to be up.</i>

03:05.321 --> 03:08.186
