10:05.388 --> 10:09.185
No. I didn't really
like school very much.

10:09.187 --> 10:12.252
Can't imagine why anyone would
voluntarily sign up for more of it.

10:14.953 --> 10:17.286
But I like learning stuff.

10:17.288 --> 10:19.352
I'm teaching myself
to speak French.

10:19.354 --> 10:22.185
Oh. So you're planning
on doing some traveling.

10:22.187 --> 10:24.386
